會唔寫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"不如繼續post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a601298caf3320bb8e9e20f7c03a7883b6b550","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"071802b9248b7cbebd292e0dee7c2d7756a9b5ab","tid":524310,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"其實我睇緊<br />\n<br />\n唔係唔擺上嚟下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇紙言link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:19:11.000Z","msg":"擺多幾日啦。。。。<br />\n紙言個post勁耐無update..."},{"pid":"8e7de4f3f69fc71b596e8271cd4a998e2d6a7b79","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b1d11eaf4382ff6fb6a2a48693ebe6810eb880","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71319faad3a02d88d5acec1f6c8c74739fec00d","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c02b08673f74be0fdb8e67e1e526fef301ae200","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"轉去fb 發表姐。。。唔會唔寫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"不如繼續post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"早晨矮巴"},{"pid":"a1aab70e66ad98dfc023fd46cc20d639702b439f","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"四十（下）<br />\n<br />\n『謎仔，你喜歡小光嗎？』小光離去後，阿慧問。<br />\n『當然不是！我只當她是好朋友！』<br />\n『那就好了。』<br />\n『為什麼這樣說。』<br />\n『在我有男朋友之前，謎仔不可以喜歡上別人！』<br />\n依然霸道......<br />\n『還有，我只有謎仔一個最好的朋友，所以除了我以外，你也不可以有其他最好的朋友！包括李小光，還有那個端木！』<br />\n李小光還可以，但端木......<br />\n『還有，假如你敢喜歡上那個端木的話，我便跟你絕交！』<br />\n阿慧在我面前雖然霸道，但她從來不會說『絕交』的，看來這次事態嚴重.......<br />\n『放心啦，在我心裡最重要的，就只有阿慧你！』<br />\n『那就乖啦，謎仔。』阿慧甜蜜地笑了。<br />\n為了守護這個甜蜜的笑容，只能跟端木保持距離了。<br />\n<br />\n『但是，我們去了案發現場，都找不到什麼線索，怎辦？』<br />\n在醫療室陪阿慧玩飛行棋時，她忽然問。<br />\n『我們該冷靜，從頭到尾梳理一次事件。』推理小說裡偵探的慣常手法。<br />\n『首先是謎仔收小光兵，令她女友子琪不滿，陷害你坐上凳腳爛了的椅子上，害你弄傷。你被送到醫療室後，她還來找你大吵一架。後來子琪被不知道誰推下樓梯，因此謎仔你的嫌疑最大，是這樣子嗎？』<br />\n『我沒有收小光兵啦......』連阿慧都這樣說......<br />\n『好吧，先當你沒有收小光兵，但其他部分正確，對吧。』阿慧的表情卻顯示，她完全不相信我沒有收小光的兵......<br />\n『另外，子琪其實也不是來跟我吵架啦，雖然最後她的確罵了我.......』<br />\n『那麼，她來找你幹嗎？』<br />\n我想過把子琪的話原原本本地向阿慧覆述，但轉念一想，又覺得子琪的過去還是不適合公開，於是只簡單說：『她是來探望我的，但後來談起小光，我又說錯話，於是惹她生氣。』<br />\n『你說錯了什麼話？』阿慧的好奇心就是這麼旺盛。<br />\n『她說小光要跟她分手，要我教她怎樣做。我用爸爸的教導，告訴她：『自己喜歡的人同時喜歡自己，是要很幸運很幸運才會遇到的，大部分時間，不是她喜歡你但你不喜歡她，便是你喜歡她但她不喜歡你。大大方方表白後，若然對方是不喜歡你的，便不能勉強，只能默默祝福她。』誰知，她卻罵我『卑鄙』。』<br />\n<br />\n『她沒說錯。』阿慧聽後，道。<br />\n<br />\n『為什麼？我不明白。』<br />\n『小光是因為放不下你，才會跟子琪分手的吧。你怎麼可以說得事不關己般？』"},{"pid":"81b9d1779ef1e6c0637d3b6475414ce28353e7af","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"突然變偵探小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446d00ca15d2191e2592fc6b1ca5a07eb93211d4","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"btw推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98f8b0b3aaba7b6e9031966744c5c24eb2c59cb","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81b9d1779ef1e6c0637d3b6475414ce28353e7af","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"突然變偵探小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"咩都有d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafdd57e464b83e9a3d4dcfe1a81db0eca981432","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3657742e79417dfed5d496816521504af59847","tid":524310,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258fb4c78e9e82a0d29c43fecb9cad089c9398e1","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3657742e79417dfed5d496816521504af59847","tid":524310,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"早晨"},{"pid":"18905abc81205ebdb723c1b7097de81e3c2f4619","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa55a6941cbe3f5547c30fcb994627c2a5e99b59","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18905abc81205ebdb723c1b7097de81e3c2f4619","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"矮巴晚安"},{"pid":"7f4f9b85cd0f40af71cbfeb17fb1512c2bcfbf71","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:30:18.000Z","msg":"四十一（上）<br />\n<br />\n『小光不是真的喜歡我的吧，你不覺得她說話的方式和阿峰溝女的方式很像嗎？』<br />\n『是有些像，但我感覺到她對你和對其他女生，是不一樣的。』阿慧說。<br />\n『怎樣不一樣？』<br />\n『我雖然跟她不熟，但你轉來這學校之前，每次看見李小光，她的眼神也好像很漠然，覺得什麼都沒太大意義似的。但你轉來之後，她的眼神轉變了。』<br />\n阿慧雖然IQ 不算高，但直覺從來非常準確，她大概是對的，小光真的是喜歡我的......<br />\n『但就算她真的喜歡我，為什麼我就是『卑鄙』？』<br />\n『你還不懂嗎？明明你就是導致她們分手的原因，偏偏你的語氣卻好像一個旁觀者般事不關己.......』<br />\n『但我什麼壞事都沒做啊。是小光自己要喜歡我的。』<br />\n『但，的確是因為你的存在，才令她們受到傷害啊。』<br />\n『那麼，我是壞人嗎？』<br />\n『謎仔這麼好，又怎會是壞人呢！』<br />\n『那麼，我該怎麼辦？』<br />\n『我也不知道呢......但我想，坦白告訴小光你不喜歡她，對她而言是最好的。至於子琪......坦誠向她道歉，往後有機會時，再對她補償吧。』<br />\n<br />\n我沉默不語。"},{"pid":"509acd9c5f9bf83c55296873fb0179c207ed7585","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e6b7a3af2917cb8b8a0cf21369a05102d399c1","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1352b2e6759fcc91603752087486172fef04db23","tid":524310,"uid":157113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"紙言無update?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785dfa752e9bcfce21f3dc7d0f87825ce533c65f","tid":524310,"uid":108524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0d59dd832c765aaa309efe9d3110ecb5f90e66","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"509acd9c5f9bf83c55296873fb0179c207ed7585","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"早晨矮巴"},{"pid":"3424091567008a27f6207642c2d93e4d4799783b","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"四十一（下）<br />\n<br />\n轉眼間，窗外的天空，已經漸黑。<br />\n『讓我們再重新整理一次事件：首先是謎仔和小光的關係，令她女友子琪不滿，陷害你坐上凳腳爛了的椅子上，害你弄傷。你被送到醫療室後，她還來找你大吵一架。後來子琪被不知道誰推下樓梯，因此在老師眼中，謎仔你的嫌疑最大。』<br />\n<br />\n『準確。接下來，我們該逐項逐項研究當中的漏洞，找出破案的線索。』<br />\n『什麼意思？』阿慧知我從小沉迷偵探小說和漫畫，所以沒有逞強，乖乖聆聽我的意見。<br />\n我從書包掏出白紙和筆，在上面寫了一行。<br />\n『第一項，『我和小光的關係，令她女友子琪不滿。』這一項有沒有疑點？多無厘頭的疑點<br />\n都可以。』<br />\n『誒 ....你和小光的關係，可是有極多的疑點啦......』阿慧奸笑道......<br />\n『我只當她是朋友，哈哈哈哈........』我無奈道。<br />\n『明明就是收兵......』阿慧小聲道。<br />\n『『陷害我坐上凳腳爛了的椅子上，害我弄傷。』這項有沒有疑點？』我故作聽不到阿慧的調侃，道。<br />\n『事發時我不在現場，你覺得呢？』<br />\n『誒......對了，那時被我坐上的爛凳，是Bonnie的位子呢。』<br />\n『所以，Bonnie也是幫兇？』<br />\n『對，可能Crystal也是吧。』<br />\n『另外，想到用這種方式陷害你，葉子琪也真邪惡！』阿慧憤怒道。<br />\n『子琪是有過不幸的童年，才會變成現在這樣子的，我們該包容、體諒她。』<br />\n『反正我跟她不認識。但謎仔，你以後實在要小心她！』<br />\n『我會的了。』<br />\n『既然有過一次預謀陷害，就難保不會有第二次呢，謎仔你真的要小心。』<br />\n『等等。阿慧，你說什麼？』<br />\n『我說，『你真的要小心』。』<br />\n『前一句？』<br />\n『誒......『既然有過一次預謀陷害，就難保不會有第二次呢。』』<br />\n『假如，真的有『第二次』呢？』<br />\n『什麼意思？』<br />\n『假如，子琪被推下樓梯，不是突發事件，而是他們一早計劃好的呢？』"},{"pid":"030aa0864f7b2694511845e0201b07cdfc2997f9","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1352b2e6759fcc91603752087486172fef04db23","tid":524310,"uid":157113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"紙言無update?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"盡快update~"},{"pid":"bf28ff78b1093dd62e22e501a74f3efe3c912bfb","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"唔記得啲人名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw留意啲引號有少少用亂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2aaa58a575bdd33c0d3506199004ff9b01f035d","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598ee38bb149d4aa8be7f3c8d09d15ecdda2e6e7","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"785dfa752e9bcfce21f3dc7d0f87825ce533c65f","tid":524310,"uid":108524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"炭巴~"},{"pid":"1eb96aa0279622c4fdfa0fd629c048cab2d0439f","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2aaa58a575bdd33c0d3506199004ff9b01f035d","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f5a050ad4774801d8322edf73930344024ed15","tid":524310,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"之前太耐冇更，停左追<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推～"},{"pid":"25e18250cdd00dde3c8a091bcf0a99b9b7831a12","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f5a050ad4774801d8322edf73930344024ed15","tid":524310,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"之前太耐冇更，停左追<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"個個都以為我爛尾。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee3f173b4a220e6353468682b5887c2b4b04e41","tid":524310,"uid":126387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"四十二（上）<br />\n<br />\n『你是說，是子琪故意進來醫療室引你吵架，然後故意掉下樓梯，讓人懷疑你是兇手？』<br />\n『對。現在往回想，其實子琪讓人推下那刻，剛巧有人經過並拍下照片，這巧合也太巧合了吧！』<br />\n『有道理！怎麼我們現在才想到？！』<br />\n『阿慧，這只是個假設，並沒有實質證據呢。』<br />\n『那麼我們便去找證據吧！去找Bonnie和Crystal問話！』<br />\n『沒證據便隨便去找他們......恐怕會打草驚蛇。』<br />\n『那麼......那照片呢？我們去找那照片看看，說不定能找到破綻！』<br />\n『好提議，我們便去找那照片吧！』<br />\n阿慧聽罷，立即收好飛行棋（那盤本來是她輸的......），準備出發。<br />\n雖然我們的推理很合邏輯，但我心中，卻有種隱隱覺得不妥的感覺。<br />\n是因為我實在無法相信，如此坦誠地向我說出她的心底話的子琪，後來會做出陷害我的事吧"},{"pid":"e5f69844afdc1cd3f09fc643f85608c339082d54","tid":524310,"uid":139373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4fcd06ce81945a4de23af4aba9aab42dd492ec","tid":524310,"uid":1263